    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a reliable driving experience. Inside, the cabin is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffs on the plastic trim. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some typical road-wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches. All major mechanical systems are in good working order, making this a dependable choice for its next owner.",
