    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, mirroring its original showroom presentation in every aesthetic and mechanical detail. Maintained to the highest standards of excellence, it features a flawless exterior finish complemented by a pristine, smoke-free interior. For the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of significant pedigree and enduring value.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
