    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65B40 4.0L V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and eight individual throttle bodies. This example is in museum-grade condition, showing zero signs of track fatigue or structural wear. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers lightning-fast shifts, while the factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides precision handling and variable damping rates. Mechanically, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively replaced with uprated components to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis remains taut, the M-Variable differential lock operates silently, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation. This is a true collector-tier specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and historical preservation.",
